articles.title: Non-Picky Eaters Sharing Foods They Won't Eat
articles.description: "I'll try most anything once. I've eaten fried crickets, grasshoppers, rocky mountain oysters, etc. I don't consider myself picky in the slightest...but I refuse to try pickled pig feet."
